{"tid":2048534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[明報] (祿泉樓)附近有7校 小學家長為周一復課擔憂","createTime":"2020-06-03T01:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T09:02:33.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae8e5fc8e6894f6651601e05dce3e71494ef6b5","tid":2048534,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"[明報] (祿泉樓)附近有7校 小學家長為周一復課擔憂<br />\n2020年6月3日星期三<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】距中一、中二及高小學生復課期尚餘不足一周，再現本地確診。爆疫的沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓附近有7間學校，有鄰近小學表示，有數名學生居住祿泉樓，目前健康良好，個別家長對復課存憂慮。教育局稱，現階段學校會繼續根據原定計劃分階段、有秩序復課。<br />\n<br />\n瀝源邨祿泉樓及福海樓（確診救護員所住大廈）步程約3分鐘，附近有7間中小學，其中聖公會主風小學位處兩大廈之間，其餘有沙田崇真學校、天主教聖華學校、浸信會呂明才中學、東華三院馮黃鳳亭中學、沙田培英中學及沙田蘇浙公學。<br />\n<br />\n聖華副校長：視乎疫情考慮延復課<br />\n<br />\n小四至中二生下周一復課，天主教聖華學校副校長楊小麗稱，有數名學生居住祿泉樓，校方一直有與家長保持聯絡，關心他們的情緒等，他們目前健康良好。她稱，校方收到個別家長反映，對下周復課有憂慮，擔心有染疫風險，校方會再視乎疫情、教育局指示、法團校董會決定，考慮有否需要延遲復課。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200603/s00002/1591123479965/%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%897%E6%A0%A1-%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E7%82%BA%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%BE%A9%E8%AA%B2%E6%93%94%E6%86%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200603%2Fs00002%2F1591123479965%2F%25E9%2599%2584%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%259C%25897%25E6%25A0%25A1-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E6%2593%2594%25E6%2586%2582&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=b765bc31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200603%2Fs00002%2F1591123479965%2F%25E9%2599%2584%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%259C%25897%25E6%25A0%25A1-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E6%2593%2594%25E6%2586%2582&h=d61d8f2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200603/s00002/1591123479965/%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%897%E6%A0%A1-%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E7%82%BA%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%BE%A9%E8%AA%B2%E6%93%94%E6%86%82</a>"},{"pid":"e1c6325463692647061f03983f94f1bc6ab7b284","tid":2048534,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"果頭仲有最少2 間幼稚園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911b1ebc3155433dbfa11936a516a71c4f1d9959","tid":2048534,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚好撚煩"},{"pid":"14f59febb800d553645fa15e02a4ac133a4e30a0","tid":2048534,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"911b1ebc3155433dbfa11936a516a71c4f1d9959","tid":2048534,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚好撚煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"你說得對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堅決支持復課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學業要緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}